# DryIoc.Messages


## What?

`DryIoc.Messages` namespace introduces simple and extensible Message (Request), Response, Handler abstractions similar to the [MediatR](https://github.com/jbogard/MediatR) project.

These abstractions with the help of DryIoc feature composition allow to cover the same field as MediatR without the need for additional library.

See the [MediatR samples](https://github.com/jbogard/MediatR/tree/master/samples) implemented with `DryIoc.Messages` below.


